title: Container label panel

claims.preamble: I claim the ornamental design for a container label panel, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a side elevation view of the first embodiment of a container label panel showing my new design, the opposite side being a mirror image thereof;
FIG. 2 is an elevated perspective view of the opposite side of FIG. 1;
FIG. 3 is a side elevation view of the second embodiment of a container label panel shown in an inverted orientation; and,
FIG. 4 is an elevated perspective view of the opposite side of FIG. 3.
The broken line showing of a container label panel is included for the purpose of illustration only and forms no part of the claimed design.
